PhpLiveDebug 0.49
Request debugger for PHP

INSTALLATION:

* copy phplivedebug.php somewhere that php can see it.
* edit php.ini and set auto_prepend_file to /path/to/phplivedebug.php
* restart webserver

HOW TO USE:

* run phplivedebug.py (I suggest making a symlink somewhere for easy access).
* in your code somewhere, put in: __('whatever');
* notice that the output is sent to your pld window.
* in your code somewhere, put in: eval(__);
* go to your pld terminal window and notice you have an interactive prompt!

